dct_title_s: Map of property fronting on the Kill Von Kull in the City of Bayonne, Hudson County, N.J.
dct_description_sm: Map of property fronting on the Kill Von Kull in the City of Bayonne, N.J. made to accompany an application to the Board of Riparian Commissioners for a grant of the lands lying under water in front of the property belonging to the estate of Amos C. Stearns. Map covers area from Ralineau Street to Avenue U. Map shows various property owners along Kill Von Kull, as well as proposed exterior lines for piers.
